data.title: Dean's Honors List - Spring Quarter 2024
data.text:
UC Santa Cruz congratulates the following students who have met the criteria for the Dean's Honors List this term. (A notation of this honor will appear on the students' unofficial and permanent transcripts.) In accordance with the Santa Cruz Academic Senate regulations, students qualify for the Dean's Honors List for a given term when they have completed a minimum of 15 units of which 10 are units for letter grade with a grade point average in the range required for University Honors at graduation for the current academic year (i.e. the top 15% of their academic group). Please visit the Honors frequently asked questions and contact us at ur_hnrs@ucsc.edu if you have questions about Dean's Honors lists.
